  • Packages that use com.amitinside.featureflags 
    Package Description
    com.amitinside.featureflags
    Provides API for managing all Feature instances

    Provides API to represent Feature instance

    Provides API to represent FeatureGroup instance
    com.amitinside.featureflags.listener
    Provides API to represent ConfigurationListener instance

    Provides API to represent Feature activation strategy
  • Classes in com.amitinside.featureflags used by com.amitinside.featureflags
